Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Flowing Away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Meijin Touji Souya\NThe Challenge\Nto a Beautiful Future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}The 43rd Newcomer Tournament\NCommemorative Match\N2008 Newcomer King, Rei Kiriyama 5th-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? What is this poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:02:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Why is the design so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's on really nice paper, and it looks like\Nthe letters are popping off the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a commemorative battle between\Nthe Newcomer King and a Meijin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parts of it have like a matte finish\Nand other parts of it are shiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A special manufacturing process?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Why are they making\Nincredible posters like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have some expert eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hired a designer to do it!\NI told him to make it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I even splurged on the printing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear it, Toku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, our posters look like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}33rd Kishou Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Only necessary\Ninformation included
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}PLAIN...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When was that photo taken?\NWhat occasion was it originally used for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The picture is kind of grainy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:46.79,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NERVOUS\NNERVOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And... how can I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This poster wasn't professionally printed,\Nbut made by the Association, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.59,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NERVOUS\NNERVOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And not only that, how should I say this,\Nthe photo of the hotel venue is strangely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no, definitely way bigger than we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}EEEEK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you treat us like this just because\NKiriyama and Souya are a bit younger and cuter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My eternal Kishou Championship title\Nis on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ETERNAL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, that poster is kind of small!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a recession and barely scraping by\Nbecause of lack of sponsors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, what was that first match?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fans won't come, and the players'\Nmatch is as shaky as their broken-down bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Can't say anything back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VIDEO REPLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Old man, one step away from pneumonia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chronic gastritis (about to become a stomach ulcer)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:56.07,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CREAK\NCREAK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.41,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CREAK\NCREAK\NCREAK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.41,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COUGH\NGLOUGH\NCOUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Sickly Showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that game between two invalids?\NYour bodies are too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it was\Nan unsightly psychological battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shimada, is the head of your King\Nlooking a bit thin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your King. It isn't getting a bit thin on top?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:33.23,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CREAK\NCREAK\NCREAK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is not thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? What kind of battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full of coughing and grinding teeth\Nand abusive language!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In recent years,\Nplaying quietly was the norm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When is your shogi from?\NThe Showa period? Are you guys from the 80s?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WHISPER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People watching them live\Non the net were having a blast, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Demo Board Commentator
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VIDEO REPLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It was an "at-home" feel with not many people,\Nso that actually made it really exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Shimada 8th-Dan\Nmoves his Silver to 5-1 left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.26,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ON THE NET
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kishou Championship Second Match
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Silver to 5-1 left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOUBLE TAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver to 5-1 left? Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just between you and me, I have a feeling\Nthat's going to cost him the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Silver to 5-1 left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}There are so few\Npeople in the demo\Nboard room\Nthat everyone's\Nsitting in a circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is a lousy move, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, then get your health back\Nand some sponsors, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Support:\NMorisen Publishing\NMorioka Bookstore\NHanamaki Electronics\NEtc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BA-BAM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! See how popular\NSouya and Kiriyama are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Shimada! It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Gakuto were the challenger,\Nthis place would be packed with female fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Kishou Championship Spectator Bus Tour,\Nincluding a lunch party with both players
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's my fault? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, we both have lousy health\Nand that game was somewhat appalling,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but however you get there, a win is a win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win the next one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone\Ntake the Kishou title away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yanagihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya is putting everything into the Meijin Battle,\Nso the other tournaments become empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one title I'm hanging on to,\Neven if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to be that blunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, get a good night's sleep,\Nand let your body rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasted my time thinking you were cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you two can keep going at it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}SOUYA AND\NKIRIYAMA POSTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get people psyched for this\Nhigh-profile match, Souya versus Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HAHAHA!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Chairman,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,please go easy on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think neither Souya nor Kiriyama\Nare comfortable being the center of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I've known Souya for a long time too.\NSo I know that about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to kill the golden goose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're facing Souya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama. There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Incredible concentration.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He can't even hear me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The precious game record!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That commemorative match\Nis in Morioka, right? Are you ready for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There's really nothing to prepare for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to wear a kimono?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, the chairman said\Nmy school uniform was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason,\Nit doesn't feel real to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! Mr. Hayashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the air around her is totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like a light, airy feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said there's nothing\Nto worry about anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's let all of her muscles relax\Nand can just rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me think about\Njust how much she suffered all that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mr. Hayashida, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I wasn't any help at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "That's not true," didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, but, how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been listening to you this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I know you were doing\Neverything you could to help her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and that she's a girl with a good head on her\Nshoulders who understands all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Results are important,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not results that reach people, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:11:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world doesn't revolve around results.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with the commemorative match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had to attend a party on the eve of the match,\Nso I met up with people from newspapers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the Association that afternoon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We took a bullet train there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meijin Souya was sitting\Nsome seats away from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His profile face with his eyes closed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No sound came from that profile,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just like the bottom of a lake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Stillness and a violent storm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}That was the beginning of four days\NI never could have imagined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flowing Away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}White Storm (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It's a much bigger hotel than I had pictured.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome\NNewcomer Tournament Commemorative Match\NMeijin Touji Souya and Rei Kiriyama 5th-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LINED UP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Thanks. I appreciate the hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you.\NHere, let me take your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Great. This is one of the stars of the show,\NKiriyama 5th-Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BA-BAAM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, why don't we go to our rooms first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOSHO LAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is your room, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SPACIOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Isn't the Gosho Lake pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SLAP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you've got free time\Nuntil the reception at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SHOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BA-BAAAM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of the baths run from\Na hot spring source,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we're going to take a dip\Nin the hot spring itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come with, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, this. The program for tonight's reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a glance at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's meet in the lobby at 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}UMINO EGG
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ALONE...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GLANCE\NGLANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The room is so spacious, fancy, and quiet that he can't relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hot spring... hot spring?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A hot spring, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it,\NI guess I've never been in one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SILENCE...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}Doesn't have the courage\Nto go to the bigger baths\Nwith everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Modern Kid...\N(Has never been\Nin a bath with\Nsomeone else...)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the program...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, the chairman greets everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then the flower presentation,\Nguests' address, sponsor speeches,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a toast from the president\Nof the sponsoring newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Players' address, Q&A session with the players,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}photo session with the players,\Nplayers' signing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reception that night was a lavish affair,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome Newcomer Tournament\NCommemorative Match Reception\NMeijin Touji Souya and Rei Kiriyama 5th-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}overflowing with people,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with lots of flash bulbs going off,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and lots of speeches being made.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. It takes a lot of stamina and will power\Nto make it through these things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been bowing so much that I feel dizzy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't think of anything to say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this kind of thing run-of-the-mill for him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Has he been standing alone\Nin this world all this time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he's surrounded\Nby all of these unfamiliar people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and steeling himself, I want to support him\Nso he's not worn out before the first match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikaidou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You always had an idea\Nof what was going on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't try to act cool, Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you really want to win, then persevere!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take better care of your shogi,\Nand yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he hadn't said that to me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure I wouldn't be standing here right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And next to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to find out\Nwhat was on the other side of the storm,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I realized how unprepared I was{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to ask that question when I saw his profile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I also realized{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I had never even\Nentered a storm before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first match\Nwith Meijin Souya, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?\NWhat kind of battle would you like to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The expressions "it's an honor"\Nand "I'll return blow for blow"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}popped into my head, but what I understood\Nwas not that, so I couldn't speak properly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would take playing against him\Nseveral times{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}before I could get a sense\Nof the distance between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how far away he was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to concentrate as I play\Nso the match isn't over as soon as it's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The next question is for Meijin Souya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you say a few words\Nabout Kiriyama 5th-Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw his game records\Nfrom the Newcomer Tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I could tell he's really studying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like how even so,\Nhe has a flexible playing style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think the match will go tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:19:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This will be our first match together, so I'd like\Nto see what kind of flow we can create.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}H-He's so good at this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GLOW...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well said, Meijin Souya.\NYou've got a way with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meijin Souya, you've been participating\Nin championship matches all year,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so how are you holding up physically?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been coming to Iwate\Nfor a number of championship matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd also like to visit someday\Nwithout playing a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}M-Meijin Souya. Could he be out of it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that answer\Nreally matches the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Okay, one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Your suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meijin Souya, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Souya, um, your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I believe many people from here\Nin Morioka will come tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I would like to do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to have a great match with Kiriyama 5th-Dan\Nthat everyone will enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone who was there held their breath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how different someone is,\Nif they're strong, your path is justified.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what are you doing, Souya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Drenched in red wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I take my eyes off of you\Nfor one minute and this happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You absent-minded general!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me! You need to get that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do\Nfor the match tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only suit you brought, right? Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Red wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can with the stain right away,\Nbut I don't know if it'll come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya, it's on your shirt and tie too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After he left, everyone let out their held breath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then someone muttered a few words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shogi demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's barely holding on to his human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, the morning of the match came.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meijin Souya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Traditional Japanese clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That morning,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an unseasonable typhoon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}went from the sea around Amami Ooshima\Nand made landfall in Kagoshima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the news said that the typhoon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was slowly moving north, as if it was\Nlicking the Japanese archipelago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White Storm (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:38.68,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 37
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.47,0:24:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He reminds me of a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.31,0:24:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Starting right now,\NI have to cross paths with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.60,0:24:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This white bird with huge wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.78,0:24:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:59.04,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ILLUSTRATION:\NTETSUO HARA
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.99,0:24:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toku, I'll take another picture\Nyou can use for a poster,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.70,0:24:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so next time\Nmake me look cool, okay?
